data.description: Embrace the perfect blend of charm and privacy in this starter home farm house! This little farm offers 3 bedrooms on the main level and 2 in the newly finished basement, with an extra room ideal for an office or playroom. The activities and possibilities are almost endless with a barn equipped with electricity and water having a history of housing livestock and chickens while also serving as a workshop.  Enjoy a beautiful in-ground pool with a hot tub just outside the back deck. Recent renovations encompass the kitchen, LR, DR, main bathroom, master bath and basement.  Additional upgrades include a new pantry, refinished exterior, electric fencing, 4 board horse fencing, a pool safety cover, back patio railing, secured pool area gates and more. Your ideal home awaits!
